author: Lisa Ryan
title: Serena Williams Tells Reporter to Apologize After Criticizing Her Winning Performance
text: Serena Williams is one of the greatest athletes of all time , but that also means she’s often held to an unfairly high standard. After beating Lucie Safarova in the Australian Open’s second round, a reporter called her performance “scrappy” and asked about her 23 unenforced errors during the... More »
